# Market Analysis

Research competitors, target audience, positioning, and conversion patterns to ground the landing page in real market data. Dispatch research sections to parallel subagents, compile results into a structured report.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write output to: {{task.changePath}}/market-analysis.md

This step ONLY researches. Do NOT design, write copy, or create any code.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Workflow

```dot
digraph research {
    rankdir=TB;
    read [label="Read product brief\nfrom change path" shape=box];
    agenda [label="Build research agenda\nfrom brief" shape=box];
    batch [label="Pick next batch\n(up to 3 sections)" shape=box];
    dispatch [label="Dispatch sections\nto subagents in parallel" shape=box];
    compile [label="Compile results\nappend to market-analysis.md" shape=box];
