## Guardrails

- **3 sections at a time** — Dispatch up to 3 sections in parallel. Do NOT dispatch all at once.
- **Web search is mandatory** — Subagents must NOT rely on training data alone. Every section requires WebSearch/WebFetch.
- **Single report file** — All research goes in `market-analysis.md`. No per-section files.
- **Cite everything** — Every factual claim needs a source URL.
- **Concrete examples** — Link to actual competitor pages, quote real user language, cite specific CTA text. Generic observations are worthless.
- **Research only** — Do NOT design the page, write copy, or create code. You produce market intelligence. Later steps use it.

